328
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,480
She is young,

329
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:53,720
but she will be

330
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:57,280
the future heir of Gu's Group.

331
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,100
