00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:41,480
It's quite cold.

342
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,880
Help Dad go inside first.

343
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:43,600
Okay.

344
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:44,280
Dad.

345
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,140
