368
00:22:48,080 --> 00:22:48,840
Of course.

369
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,080
This is my home.

370
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:55,040
I'll definitely settle in well.

371
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:58,250
