418
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,080
Yes.

419
00:26:46,520 --> 00:26:47,920
If there's nothing else,

420
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:50,520
I'm going back.

421
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,280
Yuan,

422
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:57,680
don't

423
00:26:58,680 --> 00:27:00,120
